        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-08-18 15:42:01.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\n(17 comments)\n\nThe more sever issue and question is the addition of \"transient\" keyword to some fields.   I think this may be incompatible with persistence of facts in kie sessions.   In addition, if the fields are serialized in json format, I wonder if it does serialize those fields.\n\nThe other comment is the inconsistency of output, we have some logs using slf4j and others System.out/System.err - they may end up in different files.  I think all should move together, even though is more work for you.\n\nCan you verify that junits are not missing any of the fields marked as transient?",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
